# Seeds for failure cases proptest has generated in the past. It is
# automatically read and these particular cases re-run before any
# novel cases are generated.
#
# It is recommended to check this file in to source control so that
# everyone who runs the test benefits from these saved cases.
#
# Historical note: an earlier `cc ... shrinks to n = 27` seed was retired
# in commit (this commit) when the `fact_recursive_invariant` strategy
# narrowed to `0..=26i32`. The property computes BOTH FACT(n) AND
# FACT(n+1), so the upper bound must be one less than the last
# representable factorial (n=27, n+1=28 hits the Decimal::from_f64 wall
# per math.rs::op_fact D-05). A seed outside the live strategy is dead
# weight — proptest silently skips it.
